00:01:26.991 --> 00:01:28.824
the fourth century CE,

00:01:30.955 --> 00:01:33.285
you have a split where
you have the eastern

00:01:33.285 --> 00:01:34.908
and the western Roman Empire

00:01:34.908 --> 00:01:37.741
