00:01:52.966 --> 00:01:54.947
Much of western civilization,

00:01:54.947 --> 00:01:56.989
especially Europe and the Mediterranean

00:01:56.989 --> 00:01:59.529
has its foundations in the Roman Empire

00:01:59.529 --> 00:02:01.767
and then before that, Greek civilization,

00:02:01.767 --> 00:02:03.792
and the Roman Empire is really up there

00:02:03.792 --> 00:02:05.923
alongside the Persian Empire

00:02:05.923 --> 00:02:10.104
as one of the really great
civilizations or empires,

00:02:10.104 --> 00:02:11.832
