00:02:39.546 --> 00:02:43.713
we see the founding of Rome
in the eighth century BCE,

00:02:44.702 --> 00:02:48.143
and this date 753 is the
date that's often given

00:02:48.143 --> 00:02:51.047
to the founding of Rome by Romulus,

00:02:51.047 --> 00:02:55.968
one of twin brothers Romulus
and Remus raised by a she-wolf.

00:02:55.968 --> 00:02:58.032
They were abandoned and
raised by the she-wolf

00:02:58.032 --> 00:02:59.145
as legend would have it,

00:02:59.145 --> 00:03:01.027
and then Romulus eventually
kills his brother

00:03:01.027 --> 00:03:03.086
