and we don't know the exact date,

00:03:22.413 --> 00:03:24.709
but there seems to be
a reasonable consensus

00:03:24.709 --> 00:03:28.731
that around this mid eighth century BCE

00:03:28.731 --> 00:03:31.228
you have the founding of the city of Rome,

00:03:31.228 --> 00:03:33.373
but it's important to
realize that at that point

00:03:33.373 --> 00:03:36.338
the founding of the city
that the kingdom of Rome,

00:03:36.338 --> 00:03:40.157
it wasn't a significant power
on the Italian Peninsula

