The gold color, this yellow
color is the republic

00:04:16.783 --> 00:04:20.236
and then the red color is when
the empire gets established

00:04:20.236 --> 00:04:23.859
by Julius Caesar and his
adopted son Augustus,

00:04:23.859 --> 00:04:26.127
and as we get into this,

00:04:26.127 --> 00:04:28.402
I guess you could say
this republic period of,

00:04:28.402 --> 00:04:29.934
or into the Roman Republic.

00:04:29.934 --> 00:04:32.184
This is when it starts
to really exert itself

00:04:32.184 --> 00:04:35.577
as more of a dominant
influence in the region,

00:04:35.577 --> 00:04:38.622
and it continues to be a
dominant influence in the region

00:04:38.622 --> 00:04:40.336
for several hundred years,

00:04:40.336 --> 00:04:44.894
and then as we get into the
first several hundred years

00:04:44.894 --> 00:04:46.969
in the common era.

00:04:46.969 --> 00:04:48.841
So after the time of Jesus.

00:04:48.841 --> 00:04:51.008
As we get into the 200s, the 300s,

00:04:51.008 --> 00:04:53.456
this is when we start
to see a real decline

00:04:53.456 --> 00:04:57.047
of the Roman Empire and
the western empire at least

00:04:57.047 --> 00:04:59.902
gets sacked multiple times
in the fifth century,

00:04:59.902 --> 00:05:03.079
and the year 476 is what's typically given

00:05:03.079 --> 00:05:05.827
for the end of the Roman Empire,

00:05:05.827 --> 00:05:08.793
but even that's not exactly
the end of the Roman Empire,

00:05:08.793 --> 00:05:10.526
because in the fourth century

00:05:10.526 --> 00:05:12.300
you have the Roman Empire splitting into

00:05:12.300 --> 00:05:14.183
this eastern and western empires,

00:05:14.183 --> 00:05:17.811
and the eastern later gets
known as the Byzantine Empire.

00:05:17.811 --> 00:05:20.811
That goes on for another 1,000 years

00:05:22.702 --> 00:05:25.115
until it's, as I
mentioned, I think earlier,

00:05:25.115 --> 00:05:26.865
taken over by the Ottomans,

00:05:26.865 --> 00:05:28.497
but to get more appreciation for

00:05:28.497 --> 00:05:31.284
how the Roman Empire grew

00:05:31.284 --> 00:05:33.138
and then eventually starts to shrink,

